text: Whisky priest is turning into condos

Just wanted to say thank you to everyone who worked so hard in HubSpot product/dev/engineers etc. I can’t tell you how many times I heard this is like our Super Bowl. This community is amazing—and I am proud to be a part of it. I caught up with Vin from Impact Brand and Nick “f’ckin” Decker from Square2. Good times at inbound. Thank you, thank you for making this happen!
